    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver. While the engine and transmission are functional, the exterior shows some noticeable scratches and minor dings consistent with its age. The interior has some visible wear on the upholstery and a few stains on the carpet. It has been maintained regularly, though it may soon require some routine suspension work and new tires. This is an honest, budget-friendly option for someone looking for a dependable car that isn't a showpiece.",
